        <![CDATA[
            <p>Everyone should be a part of social and cultural life, because personal and spiritual development is simply impossible without it.</p>
            <p>Our goal is to attract a young audience to museums, theaters and other places of urban culture.</p>
            <p>The GoCulture app is designed to help show your friends how close you are to culture.</p>
            <h3>Developers:</h3>
